title: Fix permissions issue when sharing screenshot
message:
Fix permissions issue when sharing screenshot

I'm guessing the old way didn't work because of something similar to

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/21680905/intent-flag-grant-read-uri-permission-using-fileprovider-in-gingerbread

i.e. use of the ACTION_SENDTO Intent in a way that's not documented, and
the permission being applied to the Intent data rather than the
EXTRA_STREAM.
